Single-engine Edge 360 plane crashed in flames at Old Buckenham Airfield near Attleborough . 
  Pilot in his 50s has been named locally as David Jenkins . 
  Friend said he was 'the best bloke I knew' and was 'highly skilled' Mr Jenkins was a member of the Wildcat Aerobatic Team . 
  Plane crashed just 50 metres from a group of spectators at air show . 
 